<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Welcome to Ho Chi Minh City — ITG New Tutor Guide</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Serif+Display:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --gold: #C8973A;
    --gold-light: #E8B865;
    --cream: #FAF6EE;
    --deep: #1A1208;
    --rust: #C4501A;
    --green: #2D5A3D;
    --muted: #7A6E5E;
    --border: rgba(200,151,58,0.25);
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--deep);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.75;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--deep);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 120%, rgba(200,151,58,0.18) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 20% 10%, rgba(196,80,26,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 80% 20%, rgba(45,90,61,0.15) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  /* Decorative pattern */
  .hero-pattern {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 40px, rgba(200,151,58,0.03) 40px, rgba(200,151,58,0.03) 41px),
      repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent, transparent 40px, rgba(200,151,58,0.03) 40px, rgba(200,151,58,0.03) 41px);
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.3rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.1s ease both;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6.5rem);
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.2s ease both;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.5vw, 1.1rem);
    color: rgba(250,246,238,0.65);
    max-width: 580px;
    margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.3s ease both;
  }

  .hero-vn {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    position: relative; z-index: 2;
    animation: fadeUp 1s 0.4s ease both;
  }

  .hero-scroll {
    position: absolute; bottom: 2rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    color: rgba(250,246,238,0.4); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    z-index: 2; animation: fadeUp 1.2s 0.8s ease both;
  }

  .scroll-line {
    width: 1px; height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(200,151,58,0.6), transparent);
    animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(26,18,8,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 2rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem; min-height: 56px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex; gap: 0; list-style: none; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    color: rgba(250,246,238,0.6);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.85rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── SECTIONS ── */
  section { padding: 5rem 2rem; }

  .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .section-label {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.68rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .section-label::before {
    content: '';
    display: block; width: 30px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-lead {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ── WELCOME SECTION ── */
  #welcome {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .welcome-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .welcome-text p {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
  }

  .sig-block {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .sig {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--deep);
  }

  .sig-role { font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.2rem; }

  .welcome-card {
    background: var(--deep);
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .welcome-card::before {
    content: '"';
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 12rem;
    color: rgba(200,151,58,0.08);
    position: absolute; top: -2rem; left: 1rem;
    line-height: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .welcome-card blockquote {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--cream);
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .welcome-card .card-highlight {
    display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .highlight-item {
    flex: 1; min-width: 120px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--gold);
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .highlight-num {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem; color: var(--gold); line-height: 1;
  }

  .highlight-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(250,246,238,0.5); margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  /* ── ARRIVAL SECTION ── */
  #arrival { background: #F5EFE4; }

  .checklist-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .check-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.75rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .check-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(26,18,8,0.1);
  }

  .check-icon {
    width: 42px; height: 42px;
    background: var(--deep);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .check-card h3 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .check-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    background: var(--gold); color: var(--deep); font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* ── ESSENTIALS SECTION ── */
  #essentials { background: var(--cream); }

  .essentials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .essential-item {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .essential-item:hover { background: #F0E9D8; }

  .essential-item h4 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .essential-item h4 span { font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .essential-item p { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ── AREAS SECTION ── */
  #areas { background: var(--deep); color: var(--cream); }

  #areas .section-title { color: var(--cream); }
  #areas .section-lead { color: rgba(250,246,238,0.6); }

  .areas-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .area-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,151,58,0.2);
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .area-card:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }

  .area-card::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(200,151,58,0.05) 0%, transparent 60%);
    opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s;
  }

  .area-card:hover::after { opacity: 1; }

  .area-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    color: rgba(200,151,58,0.15);
    position: absolute; top: 0.5rem; right: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .area-card h3 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .area-vibe {
    font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(250,246,238,0.4); margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .area-card p { font-size: 0.88rem; color: rgba(250,246,238,0.65); line-height: 1.7; }

  .area-tags {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .area-tag {
    font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,151,58,0.3);
    color: rgba(200,151,58,0.7);
  }

  /* ── RENTAL SECTION ── */
  #rental { background: #F5EFE4; }

  .rental-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .rental-rules { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }

  .rule-item {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .rule-item h4 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .rule-item p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); }

  .rental-tips {
    background: var(--deep); color: var(--cream);
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }

  .rental-tips h3 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .tip-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }

  .tip-list li {
    font-size: 0.88rem; color: rgba(250,246,238,0.75);
    display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .tip-list li::before {
    content: '→'; color: var(--gold); flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── DINING SECTION ── */
  #dining { background: var(--cream); }

  .food-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 4rem; align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .dishes-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .dish-item {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.25rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .dish-item:hover { background: #F0E9D8; }

  .dish-name {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; color: var(--rust);
  }

  .dish-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  .restaurants-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .resto-item {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }

  .resto-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(200,151,58,0.04);
  }

  .resto-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    background: var(--gold); flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: 50%; margin-top: 0.55rem;
  }

  .resto-name {
    font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--deep);
  }

  .resto-desc { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── GETTING AROUND ── */
  #transport { background: var(--deep); color: var(--cream); }
  #transport .section-title { color: var(--cream); }
  #transport .section-lead { color: rgba(250,246,238,0.6); }

  .transport-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .transport-card {
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,151,58,0.2);
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .transport-card h3 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .transport-card p, .transport-card li {
    font-size: 0.88rem; color: rgba(250,246,238,0.7); line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .transport-card ul { list-style: none; margin-top: 0.75rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }

  .transport-card li::before { content: '· '; color: var(--gold); }

  .fare-box {
    background: rgba(200,151,58,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200,151,58,0.25);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(250,246,238,0.6);
  }

  .fare-box strong { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--deep);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,151,58,0.2);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .footer-tagline {
    font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(250,246,238,0.4);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-line {
    font-size: 0.82rem; color: rgba(250,246,238,0.3);
  }

  .footer-vn {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* ── DIVIDERS ── */
  .ornament {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.4;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 3rem;
  }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes scrollPulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scaleY(1); }
    50% { opacity: 1; transform: scaleY(1.3); transform-origin: top; }
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .welcome-grid, .rental-grid, .transport-grid, .food-intro {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    nav { gap: 0.5rem; }
    .nav-links { gap: 0; }
    .nav-links a { padding: 0.4rem 0.5rem; font-size: 0.65rem; }
    section { padding: 3.5rem 1.25rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══════════════════ HERO ══════════════════ -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-pattern"></div>

  <div class="hero-badge">✦ International Tutor Group · Ho Chi Minh City</div>
  <p class="hero-eyebrow">Chào mừng đến với thành phố Hồ Chí Minh</p>
  <h1>Welcome to<br><em>Sài Gòn</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">Your complete guide to settling into one of Southeast Asia's most vibrant, dynamic, and endlessly surprising cities.</p>
  <p class="hero-vn">— Chúc may mắn! Good luck! —</p>

  <div class="hero-scroll">
    <div class="scroll-line"></div>
    <span>Scroll</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════ NAV ══════════════════ -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">ITG · HCMC</div>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#welcome">Welcome</a></li>
    <li><a href="#arrival">Arrival</a></li>
    <li><a href="#essentials">Essentials</a></li>
    <li><a href="#areas">Areas</a></li>
    <li><a href="#rental">Rental</a></li>
    <li><a href="#dining">Dining</a></li>
    <li><a href="#transport">Getting Around</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- ══════════════════ WELCOME ══════════════════ -->
<section id="welcome">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="welcome-grid reveal">
      <div class="welcome-text">
        <div class="section-label">A note from the team</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">You're in for something extraordinary.</h2>
        <p>Ho Chi Minh City pulses with the energy of a bustling metropolis woven together with timeless traditions — a truly unique and exciting living environment.</p>
        <p>You probably have a million questions buzzing around your head, from "Where should I live?" to "What's the best phở?" That's precisely why we've put together this guide — your personalised companion to settling into life in this extraordinary city.</p>
        <p>This isn't just about the nuts and bolts of living in HCMC. It's filled with tips, advice, and insights from those who've walked the path before you. Their experiences, shared wisdom, and 'need-to-know' tips will be of great help as you begin to explore your new home.</p>
        <p>Don't hesitate to ask any team member whenever you have questions or just need a friendly chat. We're all here to support each other.</p>
        <div class="sig-block">
          <div class="sig">Gemma & Will</div>
          <div class="sig-role">International Tutor Group · HCMC Team</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="welcome-card">
          <blockquote>"Here's to an enriching and exciting adventure ahead — welcome to the team and to your new home in Ho Chi Minh City."</blockquote>
          <div class="card-highlight">
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <div class="highlight-num">7+</div>
              <div class="highlight-label">Districts covered</div>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <div class="highlight-num">20+</div>
              <div class="highlight-label">Restaurants nearby</div>
            </div>
            <div class="highlight-item">
              <div class="highlight-num">1</div>
              <div class="highlight-label">Incredible city</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════ ARRIVAL ══════════════════ -->
<section id="arrival">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="section-label">Before & on arrival</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Preparing for HCMC</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">A few things to sort out before you board the plane — and what to expect when you land at Tân Sơn Nhất.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="checklist-grid">
      <div class="check-card reveal">
        <div class="check-icon">✈</div>
        <div class="tag">Flights</div>
        <h3>Book flights early</h3>
        <p>We strongly advise arriving at least four days before your start date to help you recover from jet lag and get settled in before you begin.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="check-card reveal">
        <div class="check-icon">🛂</div>
        <div class="tag">Essential</div>
        <h3>Passport validity</h3>
        <p>If your passport has less than six months validity from your arrival date, apply for a new one urgently. You can renew via the UK Foreign Office.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="check-card reveal">
        <div class="check-icon">💉</div>
        <div class="tag">Health</div>
        <h3>Health preparation</h3>
        <p>Check your general travel boosters are up to date with your GP. Some unusual vaccinations like Yellow Fever are only needed if trekking in remote rural areas. HCMC is generally a very safe city health-wise.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="check-card reveal">
        <div class="check-icon">🛡</div>
        <div class="tag">Important</div>
        <h3>Travel insurance</h3>
        <p>ITG will provide health insurance once you arrive. Before departure, take out travel insurance to cover your flights, baggage, and time before you start. Recommended: World Nomads or Big Cat Travel Insurance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="check-card reveal">
        <div class="check-icon">🛬</div>
        <div class="tag">Airport</div>
        <h3>Arriving at Tân Sơn Nhất</h3>
        <p>Visit the visa department before passport control — it's to the left of the booths as you exit the flight. ITG will share your sponsor letter once approval is confirmed. The process is quick and easy.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="check-card reveal">
        <div class="check-icon">🏠</div>
